---
import DocsLayout from '../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro';
---
<DocsLayout
  title="Keyboard shortcuts"
  description="The keyboard shortcuts that matter in Pandia — switch views, compare, export, undo — plus a command palette for everything else."
  currentDoc="/docs/shortcuts"
>
  <h1>Keyboard shortcuts</h1>
  <p class="lead">The keys that matter (and a palette for the rest).</p>

  <h2>Shortcuts</h2>
  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr><th>Action</th><th>Shortcut</th></tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td>Command palette</td><td><kbd>⌘K</kbd></td></tr>
      <tr><td>Open file</td><td><kbd>⌘O</kbd></td></tr>
      <tr><td>New tab</td><td><kbd>⌘T</kbd></td></tr>
      <tr><td>Close tab</td><td><kbd>⌘W</kbd></td></tr>
      <tr><td>Save</td><td><kbd>⌘S</kbd></td></tr>
      <tr><td>Tree view</td><td><kbd>⌘1</kbd></td></tr>
      <tr><td>Code view</td><td><kbd>⌘2</kbd></td></tr>
      <tr><td>Grid view</td><td><kbd>⌘3</kbd></td></tr>
      <tr><td>Graph view</td><td><kbd>⌘4</kbd></td></tr>
      <tr><td>Find in document</td><td><kbd>⌘F</kbd></td></tr>
      <tr><td>Compare</td><td><kbd>⌘D</kbd></td></tr>
      <tr><td>Export</td><td><kbd>⌘E</kbd></td></tr>
      <tr><td>Toggle sidebar</td><td><kbd>⌘B</kbd></td></tr>
      <tr><td>Settings</td><td><kbd>⌘,</kbd></td></tr>
      <tr><td>Undo</td><td><kbd>⌘Z</kbd></td></tr>
      <tr><td>Redo</td><td><kbd>⌘⇧Z</kbd></td></tr>
      <tr><td>Commit Code-view edit</td><td><kbd>⌘⏎</kbd></td></tr>
      <tr><td>Revert / close</td><td><kbd>Esc</kbd></td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <div class="callout">
    <p><strong>On Windows and Linux,</strong> use <kbd>Ctrl</kbd> in place of <kbd>⌘</kbd>. To
    discover everything else, open the command palette with <kbd>⌘K</kbd> and start typing.</p>
  </div>
</DocsLayout>
